<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id474c5977-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a" identifier="/us/usc/t26/s7405"><num value="7405">§ 7405.</num><heading> Action for recovery of erroneous refunds</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id474c5978-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a" identifier="/us/usc/t26/s7405/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> Refunds after limitation period</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Any portion of a tax imposed by this title, refund of which is erroneously made, within the meaning of section 6514, may be recovered by civil action brought in the name of the United States.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id474c5979-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a" identifier="/us/usc/t26/s7405/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Refunds otherwise erroneous</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Any portion of a tax imposed by this title which has been erroneously refunded (if such refund would not be considered as erroneous under section 6514) may be recovered by civil action brought in the name of the United States.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id474c597a-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a" identifier="/us/usc/t26/s7405/c"><num value="c" class="bold">(c)</num><heading class="bold"> Interest</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I23" class="indent2 fontsize7">For provision relating to interest on erroneous refunds, see section 6602.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id474c597b-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a" identifier="/us/usc/t26/s7405/d"><num value="d" class="bold">(d)</num><heading class="bold"> Periods of limitation</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I23" class="indent2 fontsize7">For periods of limitations on actions under this section, see section 6532(b).</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="id474c597c-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a">(<ref href="/us/act/1954-08-16/ch736">Aug. 16, 1954, ch. 736</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/68A/874">68A Stat. 874</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
